三、教學目標 Objectives


這門課主要教授實用英文寫作的原則及技巧。目標在滿足學生未來繼續深造及就業的需求，例如英語寫作檢測、履歷、自傳、申請工作信件、申請學校資料及其他商業書信。除了正式作業外，還有許多實做的練習活動讓同學從實做中學習。 


This course is for those who are interested in cultivating their English writing skills and knowledge in a variety of writing genres, including study plans, grant proposals and other professional correspondences such as resume, letter of application and autobiography. 


四、課程內容 Course Description


●整體敘述 Overall DescriptionThis course aims to help students effectively apply fundamental Writing skills for practical purposes. A variety of writing-related activities will be implemented and application-based exercise will be emphasized Including video viewing, pair/group discussion, and diagnostic in-class writing.

